title: 13th Ave Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small coffee house located in the Cathedral area. Menu includes vegan rice bowls and a vegan caesar salad. There are also sandwiches, veggie burger, salads, and daily soup; has usually vegan cookies. Around 3 items on the menu contain meat. Limited seating. Order at window and food is brought to your table.
